{"name":"Bullet Time","type":"advance","img":"icons/magic/time/hourglass-tilted-gray.webp","system":{"tier":4,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 4 Dodge Advance</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>When targeted by a single-target ranged attack, you can spend a reaction to make a Dodge resist. Add half the successes to your Evasion for the purposes of calculating hits for this attack only.</p>","xpCost":1000,"hpBonus":6,"fpBonus":4},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Xo7Lh3ij3SNvek7l"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768687277877,"modifiedTime":1774472019949,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"3PN6Fh9X8rgUvkVB"}
{"name":"Action Roll","type":"advance","img":"icons/skills/movement/ball-spinning-blue.webp","system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 3 Dodge Advance</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites&nbsp;</strong>Dodge 7</p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>Your dive range is increased from 3 to 5.</p>","xpCost":500,"hpBonus":3,"fpBonus":2},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.dHZcjWxD8I2swoUi"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768054413858,"modifiedTime":1774472023984,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"sPvXfGSwU7La8cuu"}
{"name":"Outmaneuver","type":"advance","img":"icons/commodities/materials/feather-teal.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.6qOsvtNATUkzYAmM"}},"system":{"tier":0,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7be5c3d-7fff-803e-3ce5-f8dae89a9891\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Free Reaction, Martial, Rank 1</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Prerequisite: Press the Advantage, Vault</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">When an enemy misses you with a melee attack, you can immediately move through its space as a free action, ending on the other side of it. While neither you or that enemy perform any further actions, you have combat advantage against it.</span></p>","xpCost":200,"hpBonus":1,"fpBonus":1},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774472046283,"modifiedTime":1774472046283,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"MUh3nSIh9XTPuP5M"}
{"name":"Vault","type":"advance","img":"icons/creatures/amphibians/treefrog-underneath-teal.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.GmntEKVnDOH6It8l"}},"system":{"tier":0,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-eb50b0b3-7fff-c1ee-a3fb-91806de3670c\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Effect: You can pass through squares occupied by enemy creatures as if they were difficult terrain.</span></p>","xpCost":150,"hpBonus":2,"fpBonus":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774472053580,"modifiedTime":1774472053580,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"qsTVQiXVVuwI9xue"}
